<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٥٥ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">‌مَالِكٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2863">‌صَالِحِ بْنِ كَيْسَانَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">‌عُرْوَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«فُرِضَتِ الصَّلَاةُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَكْعَتَيْنِ رَكْعَتَيْنِ، فَأُقِرَّتْ صَلَاةُ السَّفَرِ، وَزِيدَ فِي صَلَاةِ الْحَضَرِ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>